item.dc:creator: @p00n99range p00n99range
item.description:
@p00n99range wrote:

[quote="_™, post:7, topic:288775"][quote author=p00n99range link=topic=381784.msg2868556#msg2868556 date=1247607261]

Check your brackets above the demote command.

Thanks. Ill try that.
[/quote]

You’re missing a closing curly brace before that line.

You are missing a bracket hense a } or a { above the command you have added. Make sure there is a good amount so every bracket matches up if there is one { there must be one } to match it.

We should make a team so that if one person isn’t clear enough, the other two will solve the problem!

Got it thanks. Close Thread?

In the first post, edit it and show what caused the problem, why, and how you fixed it, and make your title ‘100 compiing errrors? It just worked!’ For future reference; people who use the search bar, etc.[/quote]

Dude for fixing it, I just moved my commands and put in a }. Why do I have to say that? Just asking?
